The paper deals with a problem of phase retrieval, which is a topic in signal processing and imaging. The use of the $\ell_1$ norm and sparsity suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-categories of Information Theory (cs.IT), Signal Processing (cs.SP), and Machine Learning (cs.LG).
